WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Welcome to British English Academy B1-M08: Stories, literature and creative expression. Learners practise respond to problems through narratives, characters, plot, poetry, performance. The teacher models modals of deduction/advice, introduces vocabulary such as genres, characters, settings, plot, figurative language, then learners complete quiz, evidence upload and reflection.
